On the other hand, DFG made Ahri one of only 2 assassins that can 100-0 a fed pure tank.  On multiple occasions, at Shyvana's high point I could catch her out and blow her up in Dragon Form with 3 MR items (Banshee, Visage, Mercs) at the cost of my full combo.

The other assassin is Zed, who's being left untouched because he's on Riot's list of favored champions:

